description:
The Current's Morning Show: Prince's "Purple Rain" is a 2024 best-seller
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

On a visit to The Current Morning Show, Jim Novak, music buyer for the @ElectricFetusMN in Minneapolis, talks to Jill Riley about Prince's "Purple Rain" being the No. 2 top-selling album in 2024.

author: The Current
description:
MJ Lenderman talks about writing the song "She's Leaving You"
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube 

In an interview with The Current's Mac Wilson, Asheville, N.C. musician MJ Lenderman responds to a question about writing the song, "She's Leaving You," the lead single to his album, "Manning Fireworks." 

MJ Lenderman’s 2024 album, Manning Fireworks, is available on @antirecords.

author: The Current
description:
Watch Amythyst Kiah perform "Empire Of Love" live for The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Having broken through with her 2021 album, Wary + Strange, Amythyst Kiah returns with her follow-up, Still + Bright, released on October 25 of this year. While in town for a concert at the Parkway Theater in Minneapolis, Kiah visited The Current studio to play a three-song solo set of songs from Still + Bright.

Watch a performance of "Empire Of Love" above.
